trans-unit.source: Call the Dispose method when you are finished using the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa metoden Dispose när du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Dispose lämnar den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>oanvändbar.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: After calling the Dispose method, you must release all references to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> occupied.
trans-unit.target: När du anropar metoden Dispose, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>så att skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>upptaget.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call the Dispose method before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropa metoden Dispose innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using are not freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Annars frigörs inte resurser den använder tills skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>
